query:
select ts, mgmt_addr, meta_event_name, meta_mgmturl, events_enrichment_targetfile_hashes_sha1
                            from hive_datalake.views.dv_events_table_mgmts
                            where events_enrichment_targetfile_hashes_sha1 in ('426dc93fa10d28ca6b93f851300026c0f58128c5') and
                            ts >= '2021-10-14' and 
                            mgmt_addr = 'fao.sentinelone.net'
                            limit 1000
